messages.message: Hello, can we upgrade the version of Go in the crafting environment to 1.22.9? I still see that go is on version 1.21.13 in my env.

On it today! In the future, it would help us out a bunch if you could also file a ticket to the crafting jira project (https://instabase.atlassian.net/jira/software/c/projects/CRAFT/issues?jql=project%20%3D%20%22CRAFT%22%20ORDER%20BY%20created%20DESC) :slightly_smiling_face:
Ah yes my bad, should definitely do that

No worries at all :slightly_smiling_face: I've got a PR for this tested and awaiting review here (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/65998) -- @mfichman / @astpierre / @Aaron Tami could I get a review on this when one of you has a moment?
